dct_title_s: A pocket map of central Washington, District of Columbia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights on metropolitan area map. "A National Geographic map." Includes notes, indexes to points of interest, inset, sector diagram, and insignia. Inset map of Potomac river south to Mount Vernon on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : The Society, c1948 (Baltimore : A Hoen and Co.)
